    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's just the thing. i'm not just \"holding\" the wood. the music isn't just paused, it's gone. the very essence of what made the instrument an instrument is gone. if the soul of the thing is dead, why keep the physical part around? it feels like i'm just carrying around a heavy, pointless weight that doesn't even belong to me anymore.",
